    answer: "Sometimes, yes — repeated stomachaches before school can be a common way anxiety shows up in 8–10-year-olds, especially when no clear medical cause is found (AAP, 2020; NIMH, 2023). If the pattern is happening often, causes school avoidance, or interferes with sleep, friendships, or daily functioning, talk to your pediatrician."
  },
  {
